# # 2D & 3D Digital Media Portfolio

This repository demonstrates basic workflows used in digital media production including 2D graphics creation, 3D modeling concepts, and visual media design.

The examples highlight techniques used in digital content creation and multimedia visualization.

## Skills Demonstrated

• 2D digital graphics design  
• 3D modeling and visualization concepts  
• Digital media production workflows  
• Visual composition and layout  
• Multimedia asset creation  

## Example Projects

### 2D Graphics Design
Creation of digital visual assets such as illustrations, thumbnails, and graphic layouts.

### 3D Visualization
Basic 3D modeling and rendering concepts used for digital scenes and objects.

### Multimedia Content Creation
Combining visual elements, graphics, and media assets for digital storytelling.

## Tools Used

Digital graphics software  
3D modeling tools  
Multimedia production platforms  

## Purpose

This repository demonstrates knowledge of digital media creation workflows relevant to multimedia production and AI training applications.

